FeedPackage.Description:
The NeuronEsb.ClientApi NuGet package includes all of the client libraries necessary for building independent applications that use Neuron ESB to publish messages to topics or to implement subscribers that receive messages from topics.
The Neuron ESB Client API supports .NET 4.0 and .NET 4.5 applications.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
Initial release of the Neuron ESB Client API NuGet package.
- Added Neuron.Pipelines.dll as a reference to support creating custom pipeline steps.
FeedPackage.Summary: Client assemblies used to implement publishers or subscribers for a Neuron ESB solution.

FeedPackage.Description:
This component represents the core assembly of the Kingo.BuildingBlocks framework. It provides all kinds of basic utility features and classes that are primarily useful when developing message-driven Business Applications.
The core assembly contains all fundamental types and classes of the framework, such as the Message, Clock, StringTemplate and other classes that could or should have been part of the .NET Framework itself. It also contains a special kind of implementation of the Specification Pattern, which can be used for various purposes, such as message validation with a ConstraintValidator as well as implementing business rules.
Source code and general guidance on how to use this framework can be found here: https://github.com/wimvangool/Kingo.BuildingBlocks/wiki
